ccess Web site at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=121548](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=121548) for updates to and news about ODBC and DAO.  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Data Access Programming (MFC/ATL)](../data/data-access-programming-mfc-atl.md)"}